s|Sir William Withers]] | after2=[[Richard Hoare|Sir Richard Hoare]] | after3=[[George Newland|Sir George Newland]] | after4=[[Sir John Cass]]\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before=[[Thomas Tonkin]] | before2=[[Alexander Pendarves]]\n | title=[[Member of Parliament]] for [[Helston (UK Parliament constituency)|Helston]]\n | with=[[Sidney Godolphin (colonel)|Sidney Godolphin]]\n | years=1715\u20131722\n | after=[[Robert Raymond, 1st Baron Raymond|Sir Robert Raymond]] | after2=[[Walter Carey (politician)|Walter Carey]]\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before=[[Harry Powlett, 4th Duke of Bolton|Lord Harry Powlett]] | before2=[[Paul Burrard (1678-1735)|Paul Burrard]]\n | title=[[Member of Parliament]] for [[Lymington (UK Parliament constituency)|Lymington]]\n | with=[[Paul Burrard (1678-1735)|Paul Burrard]]\n | years=1722\u20131727\n | after=[[Lord Nassau Powlett]] | after2=[[Anthony Morgan of Freshwater|Anthony Morgan]]\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before=[[Charles Hamilton, Lord Binning|Lord Binning]] | before2=[[Philip Cavendish]]\n | title=[[Member of Parliament]] for [[St Germans (UK Parliament constituency)|St Germans]]\n | with=[[Sidney Godolphin (colonel)|Sidney Godolphin]] 1727\u20131732 | with2=[[Richard Eliot (diplomat)|Richard Eliot]] 1733\n | years=1727\u20131733\n | after=[[Richard Eliot (diplomat)|Richard Eliot]] | after2=[[Dudley Ryder (judge)|Dudley Ryder]]\n}}\n{{s-gov}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Sir Francis Eyles, 1st Baronet|Sir Francis Eyles]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Governor of the Bank of England]]|years=1709\u20131711}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Nathaniel Gould (1661\u20131728)|Sir Nathaniel Gould]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Thomas Scawen|Sir Thomas Scawen]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Governor of the Bank of England]]|years=1723\u20131725}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[William Thompson (banker)|William Thompson]]}}\n{{s-civ}}\n{{succession box \n| title=[[File:Coat of Arms of The City of London.svg|55px|center]] [[Lord Mayor of London]]\n|years= 1710&ndash;1711\n| before= [[Sir Samuel Garrard, 4th Baronet]]\n